1.  Jboots can be constantly reapplied so as not to allow as much debuffing by dragon roar.<br>
2.  Pet pathing is not as bad.<br>
3. Don't have to worry about additional mobs, since there is a lot of fighting room, they can be root parked or kited.<br>
4.  Don't really have to worry about training the triage group, since there is plenty of space.<br>
